Blackstone to Spin Off Global Infrastructure Fund, WSJ Says

-- B y   M i k e   M i l l a r d
-- 
2011-04-03T23:41:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/blackstone-to-spin-off-global-infrastructure-fund-wsj-says.html
Blackstone Group will spin off its
global infrastructure fund, the Wall Street Journal reported,
citing unidentified people close to the situation.  The fund has raised $350 million in two years, in spite of
an initial target of $2 billion, the Journal said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Millard at 
 mmillard2@bloomberg.net  